{"tid":532482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毒蜘蛛蛋一切開 百隻BB跑出來","createTime":"2018-01-18T01:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T02:13:20.000Z","uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"732054938b7603548c78e110cb0db0719504f2f4","tid":532482,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:34:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c5s7tqfxAPY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc5s7tqfxAPY&d=dYnu1y3uyfz1DBULOnZBSU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=17b787aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c5s7tqfxAPY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/01/20180117_CH_Spider_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F01%2F20180117_CH_Spider_2.jpg&h=bd9d3a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於某些人來說，蜂湧而出的漏斗網蜘蛛（funnel-web spider）可能是場惡夢，但對於澳洲爬蟲動物公園（Australian Reptile Park）來說就是樂事，他們是當地唯一利用漏斗網蜘蛛毒液製成血清的機構。職員日前用鉗子割破卵囊，數百隻的漏斗網蜘蛛寶寶爬出來，場面震撼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/01/20180117_CH_Spider_5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F01%2F20180117_CH_Spider_5.jpg&h=b7583379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲郊區Matcham的居民近日帶著漏斗網蜘蛛的卵囊來到澳洲爬蟲動物公園。事實上，該品種蜘蛛的毒液相當致命，動物園的蜘蛛負責人凱恩（Kane Christensen）表示，「我們只能利用雄性的漏斗網蜘蛛來製造血清。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/01/20180117_CH_Spider_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F01%2F20180117_CH_Spider_4.jpg&h=7bf233e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n凱恩解釋，年輕的漏斗網蜘蛛會先被放置在園區內，直到牠們長大，會再萃取出牠們的毒液，藉此製成給人類使用的血清。漏斗網蜘蛛喜歡藏身在隱密的地方，但現階段當地居民可能更有機會發現蜘蛛，「目前是繁殖旺季，雄性都爬出來尋找雌性。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/01/20180117_CH_Spider_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F01%2F20180117_CH_Spider_3.jpg&h=71373afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n漏斗網蜘蛛的卵呈現白色袋狀，大小約一顆高爾夫球，通常裡面含有100隻蜘蛛。凱恩提到，如果有機會發現，也可能看到牠們的母親。<br />\n<br />\n凱恩提到，若被咬傷用繃帶或衣服在受傷的地方施壓，保持冷靜，因為任何走動或是其他動作都可能讓毒液擴散到全身。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2763200-毒蜘蛛蛋一切開-百隻bb跑出來\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2763200-%E6%AF%92%E8%9C%98%E8%9B%9B%E8%9B%8B%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E9%96%8B-%E7%99%BE%E9%9A%BBbb%E8%B7%91%E5%87%BA%E4%BE%86&d=dYnu1y3uyfz1DBULOnZBSU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=bc8562f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2763200-毒蜘蛛蛋一切開-百隻bb跑出來</a>"},{"pid":"5d1b7309d2fda613036a3b5cdc4c7fa0cfae9f6e","tid":532482,"uid":28195,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"屌，巴士的報"},{"pid":"8c7c673a786fd8c52ef1022e29e027c573e9134c","tid":532482,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/mQGAp9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FmQGAp9.gif&h=9ebd33d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0d3b46e04639aefe63979f6ad80ccbc42c22c0c","tid":532482,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d1b7309d2fda613036a3b5cdc4c7fa0cfae9f6e","tid":532482,"uid":28195,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"屌，巴士的報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e48812620fb9913c4da81c7c3d785661c41d56","tid":532482,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3425d4a9ed54ffd7037fba5bac7a7d3b3e8d8f9e","tid":532482,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36e48812620fb9913c4da81c7c3d785661c41d56","tid":532482,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e71ba61e72d8fed6e81c56a40cca1ca4a16a10e","tid":532482,"uid":81183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:54:38.000Z","msg":"protein <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e26e86397019f719b0de603f2c1541319ccb83","tid":532482,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ce00cd205c4adc3eeeacd543175d833e34e8bf","tid":532482,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T02:04:20.000Z","msg":"咁大粒蛋隻蜘蛛點屙出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8249aa88b84eda94220475536cf57257ab5c49","tid":532482,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d1b7309d2fda613036a3b5cdc4c7fa0cfae9f6e","tid":532482,"uid":28195,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"屌，巴士的報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T02:06:56.000Z","msg":"猩賭仲衰過港共01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968ea58fe570d5303a4afa3203dccd145d8f9a9c","tid":532482,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T02:13:20.000Z","msg":"拎去串燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}